HEADWORD: Profaner
<hw>Pro*fan"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who treats
sacred things with irreverence, or defiles what is holy; one who uses
profane language.</def> <rj><au>Hooker.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Profanity</ent>⟦br⟧
